package.name: DotcomRiver_BidGit
package.summary: With BidGit addon for Magento you can easily create automated AdWords campaigns for thousands of your products directly from Magento shop.
package.description:
You don’t have to be an expert and spend hours on creating effective keywords and ad texts. In BidGit smart algorithms apply the automated long-tail keyword strategy, which ensures a higher conversion from clicks, providing more sales at lower cost of single ad.
Functionalities overview:
> Easily select products you want to promote straight from your Magento panel, using functional product filters
> Auto-control your ads display by defining a stock quantity for which a certain product should be promoted, so that you don’t waste your money for advertising products that are already out of stock
> Generate a list of efficient keywords automatically, according to the long tail keyword strategy, which is optimised to provide the highest conversion, while maintaining the lowest cost per click (CPC)
> Set bid strategy focused on clicks or conversions, based on rate automatically calculated with regard to your profit margin
> Build your remarketing list based on entries gained in PPC campaigns to collect valuable information of your potential clients and target your future ads precisely and in right time
package.notes: - updated AdWrods library and API version, - expanded help texts, - improved error handling, - bug fix.
